# ── 默认忽略 ~/.claude 下的一切 ──
/*
# ── 只放行这些可移植的规则/配置（敏感文件永不进仓库）──
!/.gitignore
!/AGENTS.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/agents/
!/.claude-plugin/
!/.codex-plugin/
!/skills/
!/workflows/
!/settings.json
!/README.md
!/README.zh-CN.md

# ── 记忆子系统:只放行文档+种子+fixture,memory/junior/ 及运行时活记忆永不进仓库 ──
!/memory/
/memory/*
!/memory/README.md
!/memory/MEMORY.md
!/memory/notes/
